# ROVEXO v1.0 — REGISTER MASTER LOCK

**STATUS: CANONICAL | APPROVED | CERTIFIED | PRODUCTION READY | PERMANENTLY LOCKED | 100/100**

**Register v1.0 is a READ-ONLY canonical component.** Do not reopen for redesign.

Primary entry: `features/auth/components/RegisterScreen.tsx` · `app/(auth)/register/**` · register styles in `styles/rovexo/auth-v1.css`

## Canonical singularity

ROVEXO shall maintain **exactly one**:

- Register page
- Register flow
- Authentication system
