## Account rules

**Required:** unique email · verified email · secure password · terms acceptance · privacy acceptance  

**Optional:** Apple Sign Up · Google Sign Up  

**Not required for v1.0:** phone number · username · avatar · profile wizard

## Password policy

- Minimum 8 characters
- Must support uppercase, lowercase, numbers, special characters
- Never store locally insecurely · never expose · never log · never cache insecurely

## Auth flow (locked)

Register → Email validation → Account created → Auto sign-in → Welcome state → Homepage  

No extra steps. Account creation target: **&lt; 60 seconds**.

## Social auth

**Allowed UI:** Apple · Google  

**Not allowed v1.0:** Facebook · X · LinkedIn · GitHub · Discord · Microsoft

## Allowed after freeze

Bug · security · accessibility · deployment fixes only — **without** changing hierarchy, UX, layout, structure, or account flow.

## Prohibited

Usernames · avatars · profile setup wizard · marketing popups · questionnaires · onboarding flows · duplicate buttons/pages · new providers · redesign of layout/hierarchy.

## Design principles

Must feel: fast · premium · minimal · professional · marketplace · mobile-first · responsive · accessible.  

Zero unnecessary fields, questions, steps, or redirects.

